## **3. Crypto‑Backed Economic Engine**  
The multiverse is powered by a **three‑layer token system**:

- **[Meme Token](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%20Meme%20Token)** → attention engine  
- **[Utility/RWA Token](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%20Utility%2FRWA%20Token)** → governance and access  
- **[Artifact Layer](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%20Artifact%20Layer)** → meaning and provenance  

Tokenomics evolve **live during the show**, reacting to engagement and artifact creation.

This creates a **self‑reinforcing economic loop**.

